Klingon
[[Image:KlingonRice.jpg|center]]

[[Klingon]] is a recognized minority ethnic group in the [[United States]]. People who are of the Klingon minority get scholarships to college, and all the white wimminz love em.

[[Image:Drsmith.jpg|thumb|right|150px| Shown here is the Klingon "Worf" as portrayed by Michael Dorn from ''Star Trek: The Next Generation''. Those eyes - I think I'm in love.]]

==Subspecies==

There are two known 'races' of Klingons. First, there are the [[Mexican|Puerto Rican]] Klingons, as seen in ''Star Trek [[oldfag|The Original Series]]''. They look like Human Puerto Ricans, but with [[shit|better]] taste in clothes and more attitude. 

The [[Newfag|second]], and more common race are the [[Black]] Klingons. These Klingons have more [[religion|culture]] than the older Klingons. They have [[turtles]] for foreheads, and have [[London|really bad teeth]]. They put blood in their [[Purple Drank]], and eat live worms instead of chickens, but still run in gangs and don't wash themselves.

==Language==

Klingon is a fake language made up by some famous [http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0645704 geek] who probably has [[Asperger's Syndrome]]. It is spoken by alien humanoids known as Klingons in the fake universe of ''[[Star Trek]]''. It is also sometimes spoken by a subset of [[Trekkies]] who may well look a bit like [http://www.fortheretarded.com/images/dc2003/DSC00620.JPG this], and who also probably have [[Asperger's Syndrome]].

All the cool kids are speaking Klingon so why don't you?

